General IDE/OS files
These should be at the root to be ignored everywhere.
.vscode/
.idea/
*.DS_Store
*.suo
*.sw?

--- Backend Specific ---
Python virtual environment
backend/venv/
backend/env/

Python cache files
backend/pycache/
__pycache__/
backend/*.pyc

Secrets file (critical)
backend/.env

Google Service Account credentials (critical)
backend/service_account.json

Temporary data folders created by the application
backend/downloads/
backend/Processed/

Log files for the backend
backend/*.log

--- Frontend Specific ---
Node modules (very important to ignore)
frontend/node_modules/

Build output directory
frontend/dist/

Local environment variables for frontend (wildcard catches all .env variations)
frontend/.env

Test coverage reports
frontend/coverage/

Log files for the frontend
frontend/.log
frontend/npm-debug.log
frontend/yarn-debug.log*
frontend/yarn-error.log*